            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>First Alpha Release</h2>
                <p>Initial alpha release of TextWarden - a privacy-first grammar checker for macOS.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Grammar and spelling checking powered by Harper</li>
                    <li>Style suggestions with Apple Intelligence (macOS 26+)</li>
                    <li>Support for major apps: Safari, Chrome, Slack, Mail, Notes, and more</li>
                    <li>Custom vocabulary and wordlists</li>
                    <li>Per-app settings and pause controls</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
